overview.longName: Companhia de Saneamento Bsico do Estado de So Paulo - SABESP
overview.longBusinessSummary: Companhia de Saneamento Bsico do Estado de So Paulo - SABESP provides basic and environmental sanitation services in the So Paulo State, Brazil. The company supplies treated water and sewage services on a wholesale basis. As of December 31, 2024, it provided water services through 9.5 million water connections; and sewage services through 8.2 million sewage connections in 375 municipalities of the So Paulo State. The company was founded in 1954 and is headquartered in So Paulo, Brazil.
